(Made using Adobe Acrobat 2020)

Edit > Preferences >

	Documents > 
		Open Settings > Allow documents to hide the menu bar, toolbars, and windows controls > UNcheck
	
	General >
		Basic Tools > Make Hand tool select text & images > UNcheck
		Basic Tools > Make Hand tool read articles > UNcheck
		Basic Tools > Show online storage when saving files > UNcheck
		Basic Tools > Open documents as new tabs in the same window (requires restart) > UNcheck
		Basic Tools > Prompt before closing multiple tabs > UNcheck
		Basic Tools > Touch Mode > Never
		Warnings > Do not show edit warnings > CHECK
		Messages from Adobe > Show me messages when I launch Adobe Acrobat > UNcheck
		Application Startup > Tell me if Adobe Acrobat is not my default PDF application > UNcheck
		
	Page Display >
		Page Layout > Single Page
		Zoom > Fit Page
		
	Accessibility >
		Override Page Display > Always use Page Layout Style > CHECK > Single Page
		Override Page Display > Always use Zoom Setting > CHECK > Fit Page
		Other Accessibility Options > Enable assistive technology support > UNcheck
		
	Internet >
		Web Browser Options > Display in Read Mode by default > UNcheck
		Web Browser Options > Allow fast web view > UNcheck
		Web Browser Options > Allow speculative downloading in the background > UNcheck
		
	Reviewing >
		Shared Review Options > Share for review using Adobe's cloud storage > UNcheck
		Shared Review Options > Show Welcome dialog when opening file > UNcheck
		Shared Review Options > Show server connection warning dialog when opening file > UNcheck
		Confrim Importing of Comments into Active Reviews from PDF Files > UNcheck
		
	Search >
		Search > Show document title in search results > UNcheck
		Fast Find > Enable fast find > UNcheck

	Security (Enhanced) >
		Enhanced Security > Enable Enhanced Security > UNcheck

	Tracker >
		Shared Review and Form Data Collection (Server-Based) > Automatically Check for New Comments and Form Data > Never (slider right)
		Notifications > Show notification icon in system tray > UNcheck
		Notifications > Show notification inside Adobe Acrobat > UNcheck
		
	Units & Guides >
		Rulers > Show rulers when opening documents (not available in Adobe Acrobat 2020, but available in older and newer versions)
		
(When viewing a document)

	Collapse right toolbar

	View > Display Theme > Dark Gray

	View > Show/Hide > Toolbar Items > 
		Show File Tools > Save > UNcheck
		Show File Tools > Add File To Starred File > UNcheck
		Show File Tools > Save Files to Adobe Document Cloud... > UNcheck
		Show File Tools > Print... > UNcheck
		Show File Tools > Send File... > UNcheck
		Show Edit Tools > Find > UNcheck
		Customize Quick Tools...
			(Click on the existing signature icon) > Trashcan
			Edit PDF > Edit > + (there by default)
			Edit PDF > Add Text > +
			Scan & OCR (1st one) > Recognize Text in This File > +
			Comment > Sticky Note > + (there by default)
			Comment > Highlight > + (there by default)
